name: Spinach And Feta Baked Egg Cups 🥗
description: Say hello to these scrumptious Spinach and Feta Baked Egg Cups, perfect for a quick and easy breakfast or brunch! Packed with nutritious spinach and creamy feta, these little bites will have you coming back for more.
instructions: Spray a six-cup muffin tray with nonstick spray.
In a bowl, add the eggs, spinach, feta, tomato, salt, and pepper, and stir to distribute ingredients.
Distribute the mixture evenly between the muffins cups.
Bake until the eggs are set, about 15 minutes.
